race.comment: SUPER FREDS (11) racing well on the provincial tracks and backs-up quickly after closing late when a respectable third over 1000m at Hawkesbury eight days ago. Bumped into some handy types this time in and gets his chance. FLOSS'S ONE (9) poorly drawn at her last three runs and has a host of gear changes heading into this. Deep into the prep and regular rider Teighan Worsnop goes aboard. Value chance. DIS IS HEAVEN (3) returned in good order and will find this easier third-up after closing late when fifth over 1010m at Coffs Harbour. Luke Rolls keeps the ride and can take this out. SUPER SIOUX (7) made good late ground from the wide draw when fourth over 1000m at Gosford. A repeat showing can see her figure prominently.
